name: BluetoothRemoteGATTService.isPrimary
description: The BluetoothGATTService.isPrimary read-only property returns a Boolean that indicates whether this is a primary service. If it is not a primary service, it is a secondary service.
content:
This is an experimental technology
Check the Browser compatibility table carefully before using this in production.

The BluetoothGATTService.isPrimary read-only property returnsa Boolean that indicateswhether this is a primaryservice. If it is not a primary service, it is a secondary service.
